---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'Live Life Customs · Selected work · Rekraft Design';
const description = 'Live Life Customs builds bespoke streetwear for the artists, brands, and crews that London actually wears. We built a site that reads like the work. Case study by Rekraft Design.';
const canonical = 'https://rekraft.design/work/livelifecustoms';
---

<Base title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Nav />
  <main class="case">
    <div class="frame case-back-wrap">
      <a href="/#work" class="case-back font-mono">&larr; Selected Work</a>
    </div>

    <section class="section case-intro">
      <div class="frame">
        <header class="case-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Case Study &middot; 01 &middot; Apparel</span>
          <h1 class="display-1 reveal-words" data-hero-headline>
            Live Life Customs. <em class="italic-accent">Custom everything.</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            Live Life Customs builds bespoke streetwear for the artists, brands, and crews that London actually wears. We built a site that reads <em class="italic-accent">like the work.</em>
          </p>
          <a href="https://livelifecustoms.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-link fade-up">
            Visit the live site <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
        </header>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="case-meta-strip">
      <div class="frame case-meta-inner font-mono">
        <span><b>Industry</b> &middot; Custom apparel</span>
        <span><b>Location</b> &middot; London</span>
        <span><b>Scope</b> &middot; Brand + website</span>
        <span><b>Live</b> &middot; April 2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Opening establishing shot: the homepage, brand register at first glance. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section case-shot-section--first">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/llc/hero.jpg" alt="Live Life Customs homepage, off-black canvas with electric cyan headline and the chimp brand mark" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The ambition</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Streetwear gets <em class="italic-accent">a real shopfront.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="case-prose fade-up">
          <p>Live Life Customs has built a London streetwear practice the hard way: heat press, iron-on vinyl, embroidery, stickers, signage. Real product, real clients, real work that gets worn at events and in lookbooks across the city.</p>
          <p>What they did not have was a digital presence that read the same way. They needed a site bold enough to match the cut and sew, useful enough to actually convert browsers into orders, honest about how the studio actually takes work in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Featured client work: Curmah Joseph's Dark Paradise label. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/llc/curmah.jpg" alt="Featured client work, Curmah Joseph's Dark Paradise label produced by Live Life Customs" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The approach</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            The DM is <em class="italic-accent">the door.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <div class="case-prose fade-up">
          <p>Live Life Customs takes orders only through Instagram, by design. Their buyer is already on Instagram every day, talking to friends, watching the city's culture move, sliding into DMs.</p>
          <p>So we built a site that honours that channel. No contact form. No email. No phone tree. Every interaction points at the conversation that already converts. The site shows the work, sets the tone, and gets out of the way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Portfolio depth: more of the work, real lookbook material. */}
    <section class="case-shot-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <figure class="case-shot fade-up">
          <img src="/images/work/llc/samesame.jpg" alt="Live Life Customs portfolio piece, real client product photography from a recent build" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-block">
      <div class="frame case-text">
        <header class="case-block-head fade-up">
          <span class="eyebrow">The outcome</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Built to <em class="italic-accent">walk the room.</em>
          </h2>
        </header>
        <ol class="case-list">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">01</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">A streetwear brand world</h3>
            <p>Off-black canvas, electric cyan pulled from the chimp mascot, hot orange for the hits. Display type that punches at every tier. Visitors land on a brand that feels lived in, not designed for them after the fact.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">02</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">The portfolio is the proof</h3>
            <p>Eleven real client cases, real product photography, every image owned by the studio. Featured: Curmah Joseph's Dark Paradise label. The work sells itself, and visitors browse it like a lookbook before they think about ordering.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-list-num font-mono">03</span>
            <h3 class="display-3">One channel, no friction</h3>
            <p>Every CTA points at Instagram DMs. People who buy custom streetwear already live there. Conversion happens where conversation already happens, and the site stops trying to invent a second funnel.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-stats-section">
      <div class="frame">
        <ul class="case-stats">
          <li class="fade-up">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>11</em> case studies</div>
            <p>Real client work, real product photography. Every image owned by the studio, never stock.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="1">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>6</em> services priced</div>
            <p>Heat press, iron-on vinyl, embroidery, stickers, signage, and custom builds. Each with a starting price on the page so the buyer arrives informed.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="fade-up" data-d="2">
            <span class="case-stat-k font-mono">Live now</span>
            <div class="case-stat-big font-display"><em>1</em> channel</div>
            <p>Instagram DMs. No contact form, no email, no phone. Every conversation lands where the studio already converts.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section case-cta">
      <div class="frame">
        <div class="case-cta-inner">
          <span class="eyebrow">Next case study</span>
          <h2 class="display-2 reveal-words" data-reveal-headline>
            Want to be <em class="italic-accent">next?</em>
          </h2>
          <p class="lead fade-up">
            We take on a small number of bespoke projects each quarter. If you have something serious to build, let's talk.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:mark@rekraft.design?subject=Project%20Enquiry" class="btn btn-primary case-cta-btn fade-up">
            Start a conversation <span class="case-arrow-up">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/#work" class="case-back-bottom font-mono">&larr; All selected work</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  /* Back link */
  .case-back-wrap { padding-top: clamp(96px, 12vw, 140px); }
  .case-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  /* Hero */
  .case-intro { padding-block: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px) clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px); }
  .case-head { display: grid; gap: 24px; max-width: 1080px; }
  .case-cta-link { justify-self: start; margin-top: 8px; }
  .case-arrow-up { display: inline-block; transition: transform .4s var(--ease-out-expo); }
  .btn:hover .case-arrow-up { transform: translate(3px, -3px); }

  /* Meta strip */
  .case-meta-strip {
    border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding-block: 16px;
  }
  .case-meta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(16px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
  }
  .case-meta-inner b {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  /* Curated screenshot reveal — matches FUSA case study pattern.
     Editorial cards with subtle lift and soft shadow. Natural aspect
     ratio per image for editorial rhythm. */
  .case-shot-section {
    padding-block: clamp(48px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-shot-section--first {
    padding-top: clamp(56px, 8vw, 100px);
  }
  .case-shot {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.32);
    transition: transform .5s var(--ease-out-expo), box-shadow .5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-shot:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 40px 120px -40px rgba(20, 20, 24, 0.42);
  }
  .case-shot img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* Editorial section blocks — text-only ambition / approach / outcome */
  .case-block {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(64px, 8vw, 120px);
  }
  .case-text {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-block-head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  }
  .case-block-head .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
  }
  .case-block-head h2 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .case-prose {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 0.6vw + 14px, 20px);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* Outcome list — three numbered items */
  .case-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .case-list li {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px) 0;
    padding-left: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    column-gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);
    row-gap: 14px;
    align-items: baseline;
    transition: background .5s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-list li:hover { background: var(--color-surface); }
  .case-list-num {
    grid-row: span 2;
    color: var(--color-lime);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .case-list h3 { color: var(--color-ink); }
  .case-list p {
    grid-column: 2;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 0.6vw + 12px, 18px);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* Live-now stats */
  .case-stats-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-block: clamp(56px, 6vw, 88px);
  }
  .case-stats {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 40px);
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .case-stats li {
    padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--color-card);
    transition: border-color .25s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .25s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-stats li:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-active);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .case-stat-k {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .case-stat-big {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 2.4vw + 16px, 44px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .case-stat-big em {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .case-stats li p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .case-cta {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .case-cta-inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    justify-items: center;
  }
  .case-cta-inner .lead { max-width: 56ch; }
  .case-cta-btn { justify-self: center; }
  .case-back-bottom {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    transition: color .35s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .case-back-bottom:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .case-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .case-list li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; padding-left: 20px; }
    .case-list-num { grid-row: auto; padding-top: 0; }
    .case-list p { grid-column: 1; }
    .case-shot { border-radius: 10px; }
  }
</style>
